p: DIBEt was dissolved in deionized water and then diluted with HPLC-grade ethanol at 10 mg/mL concentration for PSI-tandem MS (MS/MS). The sample solution was vortexed for 1 min and sonicated for 5 min in a Powersonic 410 sonication bath (Hwashin Technology Co., Gyeonggi, Korea) for a homogeneous mixture.
